title: Bobby Reveals Valentine’s Day Surprise To His Girlfriend + Amy Takes ‘Generation Z’ Vocabulary Test + Raymundo Shares His Genius Love Advice
itunes:title: Bobby Reveals Valentine’s Day Surprise To His Girlfriend + Amy Takes ‘Generation Z’ Vocabulary Test + Raymundo Shares His Genius Love Advice
description:
Bobby finally reveals what he did to celebrate Valentine’s Day early with girlfriend. Amy takes a quiz to see how many ‘Gen Z’ words she knows that her kids are using. Plus, Raymundo shares some interesting love advice that he claims helped him realize he wanted to get married.
